BRIEF-Garda Diversified Property Fund Announces $41 Mln Acquisition Of Industrial Property

Stock Markets 1 hour ago (Sep 20, 2019 17:20)

© Reuters. BRIEF-Garda Diversified Property Fund Announces $41 Mln Acquisition Of Industrial Property Sept 20 (Reuters) - Garda Diversified Property Fund : * ANNOUNCES $41 MILLION ACQUISITION OF INDUSTRIAL PROPERTY AT MORNINGSIDE * DECLARED A 2.25 CENTS PER UNIT DISTRIBUTION FOR QUARTER ENDING SEPT. 30 * ANNOUNCES INTERNALISATION PROPOSAL TO CREATE GARDA PROPERTY GROUP
